						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1454 (1532 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Registers a gift of land in the village Aṇilai by <hi rend="bold">Tirumalai-ammaṉ who told (i.e. was the author of) Bhaktasañjīvi</hi> as an endowment for maintaining the Śrīvaishṇavas who recited the same before the god. The details of the date viz., <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1454, Nandana, Kaṉṉi śu. 13, Thursday, Śadaiyam</hi> regularly correspond to <hi rend="bold">1532 A.D., September 12, Thursday, ·40, ·54.</hi></p>						

